snippet: Nicolas Batum had 20 points and 10 rebounds, Wesley Matthews scored 18 points, and the Portland Trail Blazers overcame poor-shooting nights by their two All-Stars to beat the New York Knicks 94-90 on Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Blazers Shoot Poorly but Hold Off Knicks, 94-90
headline.main: Blazers Shoot Poorly but Hold Off Knicks, 94-90

lead_paragraph: Nicolas Batum had 20 points and 10 rebounds, Wesley Matthews scored 18 points, and the Portland Trail Blazers overcame poor-shooting nights by their two All-Stars to beat the New York Knicks 94-90 on Wednesday.
